*倍耐力在2016年改變他們供應輪胎的方式，每場比賽會帶上三種配方而非原先的兩種，並允許車隊自由選擇任兩種他們想使用的配方。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jamesallenonf1.com/2015/11/strategy-variation-the-key-in-f1-as-pirelli-prepares-to-test-ultrasoft-tyre-for-2016/|title=Strategy variation the key in F1 as Pirelli prepares to test ultrasoft tyre for 2016|first=Alex|last=Kalinauckas|work=James Allen on F1|publisher=James Allen|date=2015-11-05|accessdate=2015-11-06|archive-date=2018-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907183446/https://www.jamesallenonf1.com/2015/11/strategy-variation-the-key-in-f1-as-pirelli-prepares-to-test-ultrasoft-tyre-for-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="3 compounds"/><ref>{{cite web |last1=Parkes |first1=Ian |title=F1 tyre choices to be kept secret until two weeks before GPs in 2016 |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/122116 |website=autosport.com |accessdate=2015-12-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151204103316/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/122116 |archivedate=2015-12-04 |date=2015-12-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>倍耐力將會「指定」兩套配方在正賽時使用，以及一套（倍耐力所選三種配方中最軟的一種）提供給進入Q3的車隊使用。車手則可在此三種配方中決定剩餘的十套輪胎選擇，且在正賽當中必須用上至少兩種不同的乾胎配方，而其中一種得是倍耐力所「指定」兩種配方之一。<ref name="WMSC Dec 2015">{{cite news|url=http://www.fia.com/news/fia-announces-world-motor-sport-council-decisions-0|title=FIA Announces World Motor Sport Council Decisions|date=2015-12-02|work=fia.com|publisher=[[FIA|FIA]]|accessdate=2016-02-26|archive-date=2016-02-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229153701/http://www.fia.com/news/fia-announces-world-motor-sport-council-decisions-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>
